7. A web differential gear comprising: 
a taking out side rotation shaft with a web wound around for taking out the wound around web; 
a pressuring unit which pressures the taking out web against the surface of a subject to be cleaned; 
a taking up side rotation shaft for taking up the web pressured against the surface; and 
a load applying unit which directly applies a rotation load of 150 gf·cm or more on the taking out side rotation shaft of the web.

16. An image formation apparatus capable of cleaning a fixing roller using a web differential gear comprising: 
a taking out side rotation shaft with a web wound around for taking out the wound around web; 
a pressuring unit which pressures the taking out web against the surface of a subject to be cleaned; 
a taking up side rotation shaft for taking up the web pressured against the surface; and 
a load applying unit which directly applies a rotation load of 150 gf·cm or more on the taking out side rotation shaft of the web.
